          h1 What Happens in the First 24 Hours Without Alcohol? A Real Timeline
          p.lead The first day without alcohol is the hardest day you will ever love yourself for surviving. Here is exactly what to expect, hour by hour, so nothing catches you off guard.
          .hero-badges
            .hero-badge
